        リポジトリ: <a href="https://dev.azure.com/nightonly/_git/rails-app-origin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://dev.azure.com/nightonly/_git/rails-app-origin</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
